 "bull": {
  "claim": "Micron is the model's #1 name in all of Technology (9.66/12, Strong Buy, rank 1 of 201) and still trades 28.6% BELOW composite fair value at 6.0x forward earnings - the HBM era has structurally re-priced memory economics and the market is still using the old cycle's yardstick.",
