   "The earnings power is measured, not promised: net margin 4.9% -> 68.1% across eight quarters, revenue +346% YoY latest with EPS +1398% - and at 20.4x TRAILING / 6.0x forward with PEG 0.14, the price hasn't kept up with the income statement.",
   "42 analysts, 1.42 recommendation score, mean target +64.4% above spot - the street's own numbers imply the model's undervaluation verdict rather than contradicting it.",
   "Gross margin 72.6% is commodity-DRAM-cycle-proof territory - that is HBM/AI mix, which is contracted capacity years forward, not spot pricing."
  ],
  "catalysts": [
